com.strava.i18n.pseudolocalization.format

Class AndroidMessageKey

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.strava.i18n.pseudolocalization.format.AndroidMessageKey

  • public class AndroidMessageKey
extends Object
    Represents the key of an Android message, in which various bits of data are encoded (name, plural form, array index, etc...).
    Author:
    Julien Silland (julien@strava.com)
